<text top="75" left="83" width="469" height="54" font="4">BCS – Interesting Bits</text>
<text top="172" left="85" width="371" height="44" font="10">This code of conduct:</text>
<text top="219" left="85" width="14" height="44" font="10">•</text>
<text top="217" left="126" width="894" height="48" font="10">Sets	out	the	professional	standards	required	by	BCS	as	a	</text>
<text top="264" left="126" width="399" height="48" font="10">condition	of	membership</text>
<text top="312" left="85" width="14" height="44" font="10">•</text>
<text top="311" left="126" width="909" height="48" font="10">Applies	to	all	members,	irrespective	of	their	membership	</text>
<text top="357" left="126" width="888" height="48" font="10">grade,	the	role	they	fulfil,	or	the	jurisdiction	where	they	</text>
<text top="404" left="126" width="875" height="48" font="10">are	employed	or	discharge	their	contractual	obligations</text>
<text top="453" left="85" width="14" height="44" font="10">•</text>
<text top="451" left="126" width="893" height="48" font="10">Governs	the	conduct	of	the	individual,	not	the	nature	of	</text>
<text top="498" left="126" width="842" height="48" font="10">the	business	or	ethics	or	any	Relevant	Authority	rules</text>
</page>
