<text top="72" left="79" width="940" height="54" font="4">Public Interest Disclosure: Health and safety</text>
<text top="155" left="58" width="862" height="38" font="5">One	of	the	simplest	examples	of	the	necessity	of	whistleblowing	or	</text>
