<text top="373" left="73" width="954" height="44" font="2">4. Bugging	done	with	the	intent	of	ensuring	support	for	the	Iraq	</text>
<text top="416" left="127" width="61" height="44" font="2">War</text>
<text top="503" left="189" width="726" height="44" font="19"><i>Bugging	was	illegal	under	UN	Vienna	Conventions</i></text>
